title: Michael Phelps' Reaction to Rule Yourself Spot
description: Michael Phelps and his fiancée watch the new Under Armour Rule Yourself spot for the first time at Under Armour's headquarters. The campaign, which drops on Tuesday, March 8, struck an emotional chord with the swimmer.
